<topic template="Default" lasteditedby="rbwinst-pr" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Water Supply: Generating the Grid</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Water Supply: Generating the Grid</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Click on the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Zoom out</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button </text><image src="ZoomOut.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Zoom Out button</title></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and then click on the top view of the model until the entire model area is visible. Then select the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Select objects</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button </text><image src="Select.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Select Objects button</title></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">. </text><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">First click somewhere outside any of the objects to deselect them all. &#160;Then double click on the purple area that encloses the area to be modeled. &#160;In the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box, change its name to &quot;Domain Outline&quot; and check the checkbox labeled </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Use to set grid cell size</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and set the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Grid cell size</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to 100. Click the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button to close the dialog box. &#160;Click the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Generate grid</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button </text><image src="GenerateGrid.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"><title translate="true">Generate Grid button</title></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to generate the grid. &#160;In the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Generate_Grid_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Generate Grid</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box, uncheck the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Calculate grid angle automatically</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> checkbox and click the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
